OL,7,FA 23-year-old man has been jailed
OL,8,Fafter climbing through a bedroom
OL,9,Fwindow late at night and sexually
OL,10,Fassaulting a 12-year-old girl while
OL,11,Fshe slept.
OL,13,FBohuslav Horvath used a ladder to
OL,14,Fclimb through the upstairs window of a
OL,15,Fhouse in Darnall, in and then crept
OL,16,Finto the next bedroom, where the young
OL,17,Fgirl was sleeping.
OL,19,FWhen she woke up and found Horvath
OL,20,Fassaulting her, he fled to the other
OL,21,Froom and jumped out of the open window.
