OL,7,FIt was initially thought the 12-year-
OL,8,Fold had a bad nightmare, but his
OL,9,Ffingerprints were later discovered on
OL,10,Fthe bedroom windowsill.
OL,12,FPC Fiona Busfield said: "This case is
OL,13,Ftruly the stuff of nightmares and I
OL,14,Fwould like to commend the young victim
OL,15,Fand her family for their bravery and
OL,16,Fdignity during this investigation.
