OL,7,F"After Horvath fled, the girl went
OL,8,Fdownstairs at around midnight to tell
OL,9,Fher mother, who was still up, what had
OL,10,Fhappened. After searching the house
OL,11,Fand finding no sign of the offender,
OL,12,Fthey concluded it must have been a
OL,13,Fterrible dream.
