OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,F"However, when the young victim
OL,8,Fcontinued to show signs of distress
OL,9,Fthe next day, a report was made to the
OL,10,Fpolice. On arrival, we found a ladder
OL,11,Flying on the grass in the back garden
OL,12,Fand later confirmed this had been used
OL,13,Fto climb into the first floor of the
OL,14,Fhouse.
