OL,7,F"Our SOCO (scenes of crime officer)
OL,8,Fcarried out a number of enquiries and
OL,9,Fdiscovered two fingerprints, which we
OL,10,Fquickly matched to Horvath. He was
OL,11,Fpromptly arrested. In interview, he
OL,12,Fadmitted using the ladder to climb
OL,13,Finto the house but denied touching the
OL,14,Fyoung girl. We knew this was untrue
OL,15,Fand despite it being 'one word against
OL,16,Fanother', the evidence on board
OL,17,Fensured this dangerous predator had no
OL,18,Fchoice but to plead guilty."
