OL,7,FHorvath of Basford Street, Sheffield,
OL,8,Fwas found guilty of one count of
OL,9,Fsexual assault by touching and
OL,10,Fburglary in relation to the attack on
OL,11,F15 May last year.
OL,13,FHe has been sentenced to 10 years in
OL,14,Fprison and has been subjected to a
OL,15,FSexual Harm Prevention Order, a
OL,16,Frestraining order and will be on the
OL,17,Fsex offenders' register for life.
